    "longBusinessSummary": "3-2 Investment And Construction Joint Stock Company engages in the construction business in Vietnam. The company is involved in planting rubber trees, green trees, and urban lawns; drainage and wastewater treatment activities; installation of machinery and industrial equipment; wholesale of materials, installation equipment in construction, and iron and steel; real estate business; lease of land, offices, houses, and workshops; investment and business in roads and bridges, waterway, and road ferry bridges; manufacture of beds, cabinets, tables, and chairs; construction of lighting system; installation of low-voltage grids and substations, protection equipment, alarm, fire protection system, lightning protection system for construction works; forging, stamping, pressing, and rolling metal works; metal powder refining; mechanical processing; and buying and selling telecommunications equipment and audio-visual equipment. It also engages in the warehousing activities; exploiting of stone, sand, gravel, soil, and clay; construction consultancy; design of civil and industrial construction; road traffic works; architectural design of works; interior and exterior design works; landscape design and structural design of works; electrical design and electromechanical works; design of water supply and drainage; ventilation design and heat supply activities; design information network and communication in construction works; fire protection designing; capital contribution and buying shares; loading and unloading goods by road; cargo weighing activities related to transportation; transport of goods by road; and motor vehicle rental activities. The company was formerly known as CIC39 Corporation and changed its name to3-2 Investment And Construction Joint Stock Company in June 2025. 3-2 Investment And Construction Joint Stock Company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Thuan An, Vietnam.",
